import React from 'react' import flightContent from "../context/FlightContext"; const Flightitem = (props) => { const {flight} = props const content = useContext(flightContent) const { bookFlight} = content return (
{flight.flightname}
{flight.flightnumber}
{flight.departuretime}
{flight.from}
{flight.arrivaltime}
{flight.to}
₹{flight.price}
) } export default Flightitem
